data.description: Welcome Home! This 3/2.5/2 is conveniently located on a cul-de-sac street next to a large retention pond which is great for dog walks or fetch! Speaking of dogs, this one has a doggie door making it easy for your furry friend to enjoy the ac when needed! Your family will love making memories in this open concept! Everyone's included in the family get togethers whether they're in the living room, kitchen, or sitting at the dining room table! There's nothing better than a home with a large open concept! And this one has it! Need some privacy? Escape to the 1st floor office or to the game room upstairs. Yes! You can watch your movie while the kiddos watch their movie upstairs! It's perfect for parents looking for a master with an en-suite on the first floor! This one is a must see! A lucky family will soon be calling this HOME!
